    Abstract binary indicator.
    GenerationalDistance
    The Generational Distance (GD) measures how far the Pareto front is from the second (true) Pareto front.Objective values in the range [0,1] are recommended to compute distances.
    Indicator
    Abstract indicator for measure the quality of the Pareto front.
    R2
    The R2 indicator compares the quality of the Pareto front approximation and the second (true) Pareto front in terms of the proximity to a reference point.
    Spread
    The Spread indicator measures the extent of the Pareto front approximation with respect to the true Pareto front.
